Utterance.UttText: In bed 16, Monique Chen, 80 yrs old under Dr Francis, came in with haemmorrhagic stroke, history of hypertension, diabetes, CHD, PVD, and UTIs. on insulin,qid bgls, ongoing thrombolysis, ongoing neuro obs, all meds given. need 2 assists with adls and incontinent of urine and faeces.
